WEBVTT

00:05:29.014 --> 00:05:34.289
I had no idea about what I would do there.

00:05:34.289 --> 00:05:41.569
And I just had one phone number, actually,

00:05:41.569 --> 00:05:43.064
of one person.

00:05:43.064 --> 00:05:44.407
Three months later,

00:05:44.407 --> 00:05:48.735
after traveling all around the 
country, I had recorded 33 films,

00:05:48.735 --> 00:05:51.755
only with the help of local people,

00:05:51.755 --> 00:05:54.217
only with the help of people

00:05:54.217 --> 00:05:56.469
that I was asking all the 
time the same question:

00:05:56.469 --> 00:06:01.515
What is important to record here today?